des:
WATK 98.7 FM & 900 AM
ANTIGO’S CLASSIC HITS LAKES 98.7
LAKES 98.7 radio music from the 1970s through the 1980s features a treasure trove of iconic songs that have stood the test of time and continue to evoke nostalgia among listeners. This era produced a wide range of musical styles, from rock and pop to disco and soul, leaving a lasting impact on the music landscape.
Classic Hits radio music from the 1970s through the 1980s presents a rich tapestry of timeless songs that continue to resonate with audiences across generations. These songs, with their memorable melodies and emotional resonance, have secured their places as enduring classics in the history of popular music.
Example songs include "Bohemian Rhapsody" by Queen, "Hotel California" by The Eagles, “Billie Jean” by Michael Jackson, “Go Your Own Way” by Fleetwood Mac, “Don’t Stop Believin’” by Journey, and “Livin’ On A Prayer” by Bon Jovi.
Feature Programming: Antigo Red Robin High School Sports, Local News and Sports, Weather.
Over the Air Coverage: Langlade County Wisconsin
